content.rendered:
Leena Klammer, suffering from psychological disorders, organizes an escape from an Estonian mental hospital, then steals the identity of the missing daughter of a wealthy family and travels to the United States. However, Leena’s new life as Esther takes an unexpected turn, as she finds herself facing a mother who can protect her family at any cost.

Directed By William Brent Bell

Written By David Coggeshall. David Leslie Johnson-McGoldrick. Alex Mace

Stars: Isabelle Fuhrman. Julia Stiles. Rossif Sutherland
